snippet.title: Jam in a Band | Toca Band | Gameplay Trailer | @TocaBoca
snippet.description:
Never miss a new trailer ★ SUBSCRIBE ★ http://bit.ly/Subscribe_Now_TocaBoca
 ** Toca Band is FREE on the App Store: http://bit.ly/get_tocaband **

Play with sounds and create your own band!
The characters are getting ready for their big concert and need your help to mix beats and sounds for their performance!


Listen to the song and remix:
➤ iTunes:  http://itunes.apple.com/us/album/toca-band-single/id560550111
➤ Spotify: http://open.spotify.com/album/0GDzjYW6W7saNWnaTWv7DR

Music by Håkan Lidbo - http://hakanlidbo.com
